<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8326613>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Calostoma naaxtututs (a–b) and C. tooteic (c–f). a. Gasterocarp appearance (Holotype), showing color variation (in the top right corner). b) Scanning electronic microphotography showing the ornamentation pattern of spores; c–d) Gasterocarp appearance (Holotype), showing colour variation in (e). f. Scanning electronic microphotography showing the ornamentation pattern of spores; (g) Gathering of Calostoma ethnotaxa by Ayuuk jä´äy women." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8326613/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

